  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nIf your app is not in focus (for eg it is minimized), then you will never receive OS notifications for the current channel you are in (so you might miss messages)\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Have 2 accounts on two instances in the same community\r\n2. Open chat X with account A\r\n3. Minimize the app for account A\r\n4. With account B, send a mention to account A in channel X\r\nResult: no notifications\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nThere should be a notification. if the app **was** in focus, then it's ok to not have the notif, because we would see the message, but in this case, we cannot see it.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: master (`7c87bc8987a1c0ed5b1237bcdb8e5cca9cb40b8c`)\r\n- Operating System: Ubuntu 20\r\n\r\n",
